      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not a \"quiet space\" thing though. it's more like... what's the point of even trying to find a space? it's like being a different species. even when i'm with people, i'm just performing. i'm so tired of the performance. it feels like everything is just loud and bright and wrong, and there's no version of life where it actually feels natural. it just feels like a constant uphill battle that i've already lost.",
